  "text": "Amabile has found seven kinds of leadership behaviors that have significant effects on employee's perceived support through the work diary. Namely 1) Supporting-Positive; 2) Monitoring-Positive; 3) RecognizingPositive; 4) Consulting-Positive; 5) Clarifying Roles and Objectives; 6) Monitoring-Negative and 7) Problem Solving-Negative [CITATION_1] .",
